WEBVTT

00:02.250 --> 00:05.959
Nobody's saying the Chatsworth Estate
is the Garden of Eden

00:06.010 --> 00:10.447
but it's been a good home to us -
to me, Frank Gallagher, and me kids,

00:10.490 --> 00:16.201
who l'm proud of, cos every single
one of 'em reminds me a little of me.

00:16.250 --> 00:20.766
They can all think for themselves,
which they've got me to thank for.

00:20.810 --> 00:21.925
Quick, leg it!

00:21.970 --> 00:24.325
Lip, who's a bit of a gobshite,
which is why nobody calls him

00:24.370 --> 00:26.361
Phillip any more.

00:26.410 --> 00:28.878
lan, a lot like his mam,
which is handy for the others

00:28.930 --> 00:31.398
cos she's disappeared into thin air.

00:31.450 --> 00:34.248
And Carl - we daren't let him
grow his hair for two reasons.

00:34.290 --> 00:36.440
One, it makes it stand on end
and makes him look like Toyah.

00:36.490 --> 00:42.122
Two, nits love it. Debbie, sent by
God, total angel - you've to check

00:42.170 --> 00:45.685
your change but she'll go miles
out of her way to do you a favour.

00:45.730 --> 00:48.449
Plus lickle Liam,
who's gonna be a star some day.

00:48.490 --> 00:50.685
Sheila, me bird,
couldn't be happier,

00:50.730 --> 00:52.402
one plate short of a full set, like.

00:52.450 --> 00:56.329
And fantastic neighbours
Kev and Veronica,

00:56.370 --> 00:58.725
lend ya anything,
well, almost anything.

00:58.770 --> 01:03.400
Carol and Marty, the lodgers from hell.
Last of the lonely hearts

01:03.450 --> 01:06.522
and a psychologist's wet dream.
Still, nobody's perfect.

01:06.570 --> 01:10.927
But all of 'em to a man know,
first and foremost,

01:10.970 --> 01:15.919
one of the most vital necessities in life is,
they know how to throw a party!

01:15.970 --> 01:17.198
Scatter!

01:19.130 --> 01:21.405
(Frank) 'Me first stag night,
the barman tells me a joke.

01:21.450 --> 01:24.567
'Kid goes up to his dad, says
he's heard that in some countries,

01:24.610 --> 01:26.362
'a man doesn't even know his
wife till he marries her.

01:26.410 --> 01:29.925
'His dad tells him, ''That happens
in every fucking country, son.''

01:29.970 --> 01:33.007
'And it's true, innit?
l mean, if l'd have known Monica

01:33.050 --> 01:35.928
'was gonna be a lezzer,
l'd never have married her, would l?

01:35.970 --> 01:41.124
'Well, yeah, probably, l mean, l'd have thought
l was in with a, you know, flesh sandwich.

01:41.170 --> 01:45.368
'But the point l'm making,
is, you just don't know, do you?

01:45.410 --> 01:49.528
'Spin the fucking wheel. So that's
the point of a stag do, innit?

01:49.570 --> 01:52.926
'Cos like the chief Roman said,
''Veni, vidi, vodka.''

01:52.970 --> 01:58.328
'Numb me fucking senses, boys, l'm
comin' in!' Whoa! Not fucking Marty!

