nylon tulle veil, modesty panel.

23:09.210 --> 23:14.000
l know you don't like looking after
the twins but l thought maybe for...

23:14.050 --> 23:17.486
Course l do!
No, don't be silly! Any time!

23:17.530 --> 23:18.599
- lt'd only be for an hour.
- Yeah.

23:18.650 --> 23:21.005
Don't question it, Sheila,
he might change his mind!

23:21.050 --> 23:23.041
Anyway, l've gotta shoot.

23:23.090 --> 23:25.046
Hey, Veronica!

23:25.090 --> 23:26.318
Have you got moles, then?

23:27.890 --> 23:29.209
You what, Lillian?

23:29.250 --> 23:33.368
Moles. Our Leslie saw you digging
in't garden. She lives over the back.

23:33.410 --> 23:37.323
No, Lillian, no, it's the diggers...
We got the builders in. lt's not us.

23:37.370 --> 23:40.646
lt was definitely you.
ln the night. She wanted to go.

23:40.690 --> 23:44.603
No, she must've been dreaming it.
Dreamt it. You know what she's like.

23:44.650 --> 23:46.686
Hang on. Sheila, come on darling.

23:46.730 --> 23:49.369
(Lillian) She did tell me it were you.
She knows yer house.

23:49.410 --> 23:52.447
Lillian! Hang on, love. Just go on,
darling, you enjoy yourself.

23:52.490 --> 23:54.799
She told me it were you,
she knows yer house.

23:54.850 --> 23:57.205
Hey, your work on this planet is
finished, return to your own people.

23:57.250 --> 24:00.048
She don't tell lies. She saw yer.

24:10.170 --> 24:11.888
Fucking hell.

24:11.930 --> 24:15.923
No. No. No.

24:18.050 --> 24:20.245
Look, Lip, l told you.

24:20.290 --> 24:22.360
(Lip) Just come with us a minute.

24:22.410 --> 24:25.243
Debs, watch Katie.

24:25.290 --> 24:27.281
What we doing, Lip?

24:27.330 --> 24:29.764
You'll see in a minute.

24:29.810 --> 24:33.041
All right, you ready?

24:35.050 --> 24:36.039
Ta da!

24:39.930 --> 24:41.363
What's this meant to be?

24:41.410 --> 24:43.048
lt's for you.

24:43.090 --> 24:46.400
l thought if you moved in here,
l'll be around, won't l?

24:46.450 --> 24:47.439
Won't be able to forget things.

24:47.490 --> 24:50.243
Lip, a couple of coats of paint
aren't gonna solve anything.

24:50.290 --> 24:53.362
And what makes you think l'm
gonna move in here with you lot?

24:53.410 --> 24:55.560
lt's a fucking mad house.

24:55.610 --> 24:59.364
No offence,
but l'd rather eat me own sick.

24:59.410 --> 25:01.207
l don't understand you.

25:02.250 --> 25:04.241
But l want it to work, Mandy.

25:04.290 --> 25:08.681
Yeah, so do l.
But it's us we've gotta sort out.

25:08.730 --> 25:10.561
The real stuff.

25:10.610 --> 25:12.089
Not some fucking paint job.

25:18.290 --> 25:19.928
l don't want to, Debbie.

25:19.970 --> 25:21.562
Brian! You said you'd help me.

25:21.610 --> 25:23.840
You said l could kiss you.

25:23.890 --> 25:26.450
Just help me get
the dress and l'll...

25:26.490 --> 25:28.048
Just one, OK? Here.

25:29.690 --> 25:32.762
On the mouth.
On the mouth or l'm not doing it.

25:33.850 --> 25:37.445
Just help me get the dress,
all right?

25:45.250 --> 25:46.763
Where'd you get it from?

25:46.810 --> 25:50.325
Oh, you know,
grave robbing, usual stuff!

25:50.370 --> 25:52.600
l'd put it back if l was you.

25:52.650 --> 25:56.848
- Eh?
- lt's fake. The lot of it. Ain't worth a penny.

26:05.970 --> 26:08.120
Come on then, let me see.

26:08.170 --> 26:09.649
All right, then.

26:09.690 --> 26:12.921
But make it quick. And if you
gob on me, l'll throw up on you.

26:16.930 --> 26:18.568
Well go on, then!

26:20.170 --> 26:22.206
l think you're horrible.

26:22.250 --> 26:24.445
You think you're really it
but you're not.

26:24.490 --> 26:27.641
You're just using me, and you
shouldn't do that cos it's wrong.

26:27.690 --> 26:30.409
l don't wanna kiss you.
l don't wanna see you ever again.

26:41.330 --> 26:43.207
Frank?

26:44.890 --> 26:46.608
Are you all right about tomorrow?

26:46.650 --> 26:48.800
l can't wait to be Mrs Gallagher.

26:52.450 --> 26:54.805
l think l'll just hit the hay,
Sheila.

27:06.690 --> 27:09.329
Just locking up for
the night, Frank. >

27:20.370 --> 27:21.564
Frank?

27:23.370 --> 27:26.601
Yeah, just in here, love.

27:27.850 --> 27:31.001
Frank, are you all right, love?

27:31.050 --> 27:33.962
Yeah, just...you know...

27:36.570 --> 27:38.208
ls there something wrong?

27:39.530 --> 27:41.441
Frank? >

27:42.410 --> 27:43.968
What Lillian said...

27:44.010 --> 27:46.729
Were you digging? >

27:50.370 --> 27:52.088
Did you dig him up?!

27:53.530 --> 27:55.839
Sorry, love. Can't hear you.

27:57.530 --> 27:59.043
Did you dig him up?!

28:00.610 --> 28:01.759
Did you dig him up?

28:02.890 --> 28:04.289
Did you dig him up, Frank?

28:25.170 --> 28:25.647
Hey, erm...

28:25.690 --> 28:26.805
< Veronica.

28:26.850 --> 28:29.444
You've heard, haven't you?

28:29.490 --> 28:31.208
From the hospital.

28:31.250 --> 28:34.128
lt's not good news, is it?

28:34.170 --> 28:37.082
No.

28:37.130 --> 28:40.839
Oh, look, l'm really sorry.

28:40.890 --> 28:42.164
l just didn't know how to tell you.

28:42.210 --> 28:43.359
You're all right.

28:43.410 --> 28:44.729
< Veronica!

28:44.770 --> 28:46.567
Veronica!

28:46.610 --> 28:48.202
