playing at, Frank?!

28:53.410 --> 28:54.399
Let me in!

28:54.450 --> 28:56.281
You've just broken
the fucking window!

28:56.330 --> 29:00.482
Look... l need the
money from the gold.

29:00.530 --> 29:02.088
What fucking gold?!

29:02.130 --> 29:03.245
You've done what?!

29:03.290 --> 29:05.121
He were fucking dead anyway!

29:05.170 --> 29:07.365
Correction - murdered. How much?

29:07.410 --> 29:09.719
- Hey, you what?!
- Sheila murdered him. So?

29:09.770 --> 29:11.886
- She murdered him? You're joking.
- Wish l fucking was, mate.

29:11.930 --> 29:14.524
Well, Frank, it was a big fat zero
cos it's all fake,

29:14.570 --> 29:16.322
so fucking tough shit on both of us.

29:16.370 --> 29:17.689
So l dug up that
body up for nothing?

29:17.730 --> 29:19.925
You didn't dig him up, l fucking did!

29:19.970 --> 29:22.530
That gold was my
get out of jail free card!

29:22.570 --> 29:25.004
How the hell am l gonna
get away from her now?!

29:25.050 --> 29:28.679
- Whoa, what you on about?
- She knows! Fucking Lillian,

29:28.730 --> 29:31.005
fucking...
And now she's gonna kill me.

29:31.050 --> 29:34.565
No, it's not fucking funny!
You didn't see her with that spade.

29:34.610 --> 29:37.044
They get a taste for it, don't they?
l've seen Crimewatch.

29:37.090 --> 29:41.208
(Veronica) - Oh, for fuck's sake!
- What the hell am l gonna do now?!

29:41.250 --> 29:43.605
l'm gonna have to stay here
while l get me head together.

29:43.650 --> 29:45.368
You are joking. Over my dead body!

29:45.410 --> 29:48.720
lt's me darkest hour, Veronica!
Me dream wedding in tatters.

29:48.770 --> 29:51.921
Me kids are not taking pity on me.
Lip's already thrown me out.

29:51.970 --> 29:53.688
Well, tell it to Oprah! Now fuck off!

29:57.450 --> 30:01.125
Veronica, you can't do this
to me, l'm a marked man!

30:01.170 --> 30:03.525
You got me into this! Veronica!

30:03.570 --> 30:05.083
Go home, Frank!

30:09.010 --> 30:09.999
Piss!

30:12.210 --> 30:14.087
l don't believe you!

30:14.130 --> 30:16.325
l know. Don't.

30:16.370 --> 30:18.122
What were you thinking?!

30:18.170 --> 30:24.564
l thought we could use
the money to...for lVF.

30:24.610 --> 30:26.965
l know how much you want it, Kev.

30:27.010 --> 30:29.649
Oh, you...

30:29.690 --> 30:31.169
Come here, you daft cow.

30:34.610 --> 30:38.683
Hey, not many blokes could say their
wife'd go grave robbing for 'em.

30:38.730 --> 30:40.721
Ooh, it were horrible and all.

30:40.770 --> 30:42.408
And he stank!

30:42.450 --> 30:43.644
Ooh.

30:43.690 --> 30:45.760
Look, Vee,

30:45.810 --> 30:48.643
