We don't need no-one else.

30:51.930 --> 30:54.364
Hey, but we don't need
to be trying for a baby...

30:55.930 --> 30:57.488
..to have sex, do we?

30:57.530 --> 30:58.929
No!

30:58.970 --> 31:00.449
Let us in, then!

31:15.210 --> 31:16.484
Frank?

31:26.570 --> 31:27.764
Frank?

31:29.210 --> 31:32.327
Are you there, love?

31:32.930 --> 31:36.286
Carl...is your dad there?

31:36.330 --> 31:37.968
