31:38.010 --> 31:39.159
l think he's left me.

31:39.210 --> 31:40.689
Hey, give over, Sheila.

31:40.730 --> 31:43.688
He's...he's probably with...

31:43.730 --> 31:47.040
He's probably out
with Kev somewhere, isn't he?

31:47.090 --> 31:49.320
Getting ready and that.

31:49.370 --> 31:52.328
lt's bad luck to see you on
your wedding day, in't it?

31:52.370 --> 31:55.965
Look, why don't you go home?

31:56.010 --> 31:58.365
Don't worry, we'll find him.

32:00.610 --> 32:01.599
l'll get him.

32:04.530 --> 32:07.488
What the fuck are you doing, Frank?
lt's your wedding day.

32:07.530 --> 32:10.408
