32:12.850 --> 32:15.000
l'm a hunted man!

32:15.050 --> 32:18.042
She's got a fucking spade, Veronica!

32:18.090 --> 32:21.924
lf you're not gonna marry her, Frank,
you have gotta tell her.

32:21.970 --> 32:24.609
Sort him out, will you?
l'm going to Sheila's.

32:26.610 --> 32:28.202
Come on, knobhead.

32:28.250 --> 32:31.879
All right, so you dig up this
bloke and she's killed him, right?

32:31.930 --> 32:35.206
