he's not the only one?

32:35.250 --> 32:39.129
Remember...Eddie The Owl?

32:39.170 --> 32:41.161
Fucking missionary work?

32:41.210 --> 32:43.724
ln Africa? Or six feet under?

32:43.770 --> 32:45.886
What's the more likely, eh?

32:45.930 --> 32:48.285
Look, the only reason you
know about Sheldon

32:48.330 --> 32:50.798
