giving you the same?

32:52.970 --> 32:54.881
Well, it's a double bluff, in't it?

32:54.930 --> 32:56.488
Plus, she had no choice.

32:56.530 --> 32:59.920
No, that's bollocks, Frank.
The reason she told you

32:59.970 --> 33:01.528
is because she trusts you.

33:01.570 --> 33:04.209
That woman, she wouldn't
lay a finger on you.

33:04.250 --> 33:08.448
Fuck knows why, but she thinks
the sun shines out of your arse.

33:08.490 --> 33:11.288
But she's still
a fucking murderer, Kev.

33:11.330 --> 33:12.558
l'm not marrying her.

33:17.010 --> 33:18.807
lt's beautiful, in't it?

33:18.850 --> 33:20.568
l thought l might as well put it on,

33:20.610 --> 33:22.919
though l don't s'pose
l'll be needing it now.

33:22.970 --> 33:23.959
Hey now, come on. Enough of that.

33:24.010 --> 33:27.605
He knows, doesn't he?
He knows about Sheldon.

33:27.650 --> 33:28.878
l'm sorry, Sheila...

33:28.930 --> 33:30.921
He used to hit me.

33:30.970 --> 33:33.723
lf everything wasn't
just so, he used to...

33:33.770 --> 33:37.319
lt was like he was looking
for things to find fault with.

33:37.370 --> 33:42.000
Like, if his records weren't stacked
neatly or if l had a button undone.

33:42.050 --> 33:44.644
Sheldon fucking beat you?

33:44.690 --> 33:47.158
l was young.
You think you deserve it, don't you?

33:47.210 --> 33:51.886
You don't know any better.
lt was the gold that was the worst.

33:51.930 --> 33:53.522
He used to burn me with it,

33:53.570 --> 33:56.403
pattern marks all up and
down me arms and legs.

34:04.930 --> 34:08.400
And if l cried,
he'd punch me in the face.

34:08.449 --> 34:12.806
Battered me once, put
me in hospital for a month.

34:12.850 --> 34:14.329
Why didn't anybody stop him?

34:14.370 --> 34:16.042
Why didn't you go to the police?

34:16.090 --> 34:19.127
l did, but they used to pretend
they couldn't see the marks.

34:19.170 --> 34:21.161
They just used to
say, ''There, there,''

